content: I am so very proud of you Marvin Scott and your new book As I Saw It. With a career spanning more than 50 years, Marvin has seen it all.  From international headlines to local heroes, the eleven-time Emmy Award–winner and member of the New York State Broadcasters Hall of Fame has covered the news PIX 11 with objectivity and integrity. He has interviewed six presidents, visited the frontlines of war in the Middle East and Asia, and witnessed the rise of America’s space program―all in a day’s work. Check out his brand new book: https://www.amazon.com/As-I-Saw-Marvin-Scott/dp/0825308429
